@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qpyout(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v2 / v0)
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.31 * v0 + 0.11)) * 0.42)
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = (v0 + v0)
    v2 = v1
    v0 = (wp.abs(v0) + wp.sin(0.13))
    data[tid] = v0
